query:
SELECT inspectionId, stationKey, COUNT(*) as count
FROM tmlReadings
WHERE stationKey IS NOT NULL AND stationKey != ''
GROUP BY inspectionId, stationKey
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
LIMIT 20;
